  41:../Middlewares/stm32-mw-camera/ISP_Library/isp/Src/isp_algo.c **** /* Delay (in number of VSYNC) between the time an ISP control (e.g. ColorConv)
  42:../Middlewares/stm32-mw-camera/ISP_Library/isp/Src/isp_algo.c ****  * is updated and the time the frame is actually updated. Typical user = AWB algo. */
